vote.title: A resolution of the City Council of the City of Dallas, Texas (1) authorizing the publication of Notice of Intention to Issue Certificates of Obligation; (2) approving the preparation of a preliminary official statement and a Notice of Sale; and (3) providing for the effective date thereof - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
